<dd class=3D"field-odd"><dl>
<dt><strong>n_components</strong><span class=3D"classifier">int, float or =
=E2=80=98mle=E2=80=99, default=3DNone</span></dt><dd><p>Number of component=
s to keep.
if n_components is not set all components are kept:</p>
